      "raw_text": "INDIANAPOLIS, Jan. Lett Is\nannounced that miners delegates\nwill meet tonight to consider the\ncases of Meyer, Haywood and Petit\nbone. The federation convention\napplanded the announcement.\n\n\nA delegate from Colorado dis\ntrict criticized the national organi-\ncation for sending Organizer Bans\nfield there without request. Mitch\nell said he was surprised at being\ncensured for sending an organizer.\nHe was usually censured for not\nsending one. The protesting dele\ngate used tn eincident as basis\nOf criticism for national interior\nence in local affairs."
